---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import { currentYear } from "@/util";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p><em>Last Updated: {currentYear()}</em></p>

    <p>This privacy policy applies to all applications developed by Twizmo! Games.</p>

    <h2>Information Collection and Use</h2>
    <p>We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal information from users of our applications. All data generated or used by our apps remains solely on your device.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Our applications do not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.</p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>Since no data is collected or transmitted from our applications, your information remains private and under your control at all times.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our applications do not knowingly collect information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>If our data practices change in the future, we will update this privacy policy and note the revision date above.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at info@twizmo-games.com.</p>
</Layout>
